casebody.data:
PETITIONS FOR WRITS OF CERTIORARI GRANTED, FROM OCTOBER 4, 1920, TO AND INCLUDING JANUARY 24, 1921.

No. 333. Herbert L. Hildreth v. Jim M. Mastoras.

October 11, 1920. Petition for a writ of certiorari to the Circuit Court of Appeals for. the Ninth Circuit granted. Mr. George P. Dike and Mr. Frederic D. McKenney for petitioner. Mr. Joseph L. Atkins for respondent.
